# GrooveCommission Upcoming Musical Exploration

The GrooveCommission's instrumentation of choice for the evening of Friday, December 13th features the live trombone long tones of Sarah Privler infused with the iOS musings of Dazza Greenwood at the MIT Media Lab.  Come enjoy our performance/practice session at E15-384b before 99Fridays and we *MAY* even help warm things up for 99Fridays!
